title: Sample Book, Non Fading Wallpaper, 1931
description: Wallpaper designs in the modern style with stylized and abstract floral  and foliate patterns, rough plaster effects, cubist-inspired designs, landscapes and tapestry effects. Most of the wallpaper samples have a narrow border printed across the top of the page.

tombstone.epitaph: Sample Book, Non Fading Wallpaper, 1931; Distributed by Montgomery Ward & Co., Inc. ; USA; machine printed on paper; 28 x 21.5 cm (11 x 8 7/16 in.); Gift of Robert C. Kaufmann; 1975-84-4-1/76
